{"word":"G5093 - τίμιος - tímios - tim'-ee-os - Dear","slug":"G5093","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τίμιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>tímios"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tim'-ee-os"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Dear"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C4;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03BC;&#x03B9;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - timios</b> - <i>tim'-ee-os</i><p/>Including the comparative <b>&#x03C4;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03BC;&#x03B9;&#x03C9;&#x0301;&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03C2;</b> <b>timio&#x0304;teros</b> and the superlative <b>&#x03C4;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03BC;&#x03B9;&#x03C9;&#x0301;&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x03C2;</b> <b>timio&#x0304;tatos</b>; from <a href=\"#/G5092\">G5092</a>; <i>valuable</i>, that is, (objectively) <i>costly</i>, or (subjectively) <i>honored</i>, <i>esteemed</i>, or (figuratively) <i>beloved:</i> - dear, honourable, (more, most) precious, had in reputation."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G5091\">G5091</a>, <a href=\"#/G5092\">G5092</a>, <a href=\"#/G5094\">G5094</a>"}]}